          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（李大上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "李大",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "李大生来罗里罗嗦，娶了个好吃懒做的老婆。"
        },
        {
          "character": "李大",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "死人店铺活人开，一个去了百个来。早晨起来七件事，米面油盐酱醋柴。"
        },
        {
          "character": "李大",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "在下、李大。夫妇二人，在这遇龙镇上开设一座店房。前几天连阴天，店里一\n个客人没有。今儿个天气晴和，不免将招牌挂起，下几个客人也好度用。就是\n这个主意。"
        },
        {
          "character": "李大",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "夫妻二人把店开，\n早晨起来挂招牌。\n专等四方君子来。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（刘秀上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘秀",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "父王晏驾实可惨，\n王莽篡夺锦江山。\n小王逃走不得安。\n邓禹求救未回还。\n不觉来到旅店前。"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘秀",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "且住！看天色已晚，不免在此安歇。\n店家请了！"
        },
        {
          "character": "苏献带兵将孤赶、马武与贼去交战、行走之间抬头看、李大",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "这位君子敢是投宿的吗？"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘秀",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "正是。"
        },
        {
          "character": "李大",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "请进上房。待我将招牌摘去。"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘秀",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "因何将招牌摘去？"
        },
        {
          "character": "李大",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "君子你可知道，好客不要多，一个顶十个，这就是上房，请到里面坐。\n嗳，老婆，上房里住了一位客人，好好照应着。我到街上买点儿菜去啊！"
        },
        {
          "character": "王氏",
          "line_type": "内白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "速去速来！"
        },
        {
          "character": "李大",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我知道。\n客人少坐片刻，我去去就来。"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘秀",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "店东请便。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（李大下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘秀",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "小王独坐店房，思想邓禹搬兵未到；马武交战，胜负未知，好不愁闷人也！"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘秀",
          "line_type": "西皮慢板",
          "musical_style": "西皮慢板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "有小王坐店房神魂不定，\n想起了老王爷珠泪双倾。\n贼王莽篡汉室锦绣江洪。\n有小王与母后未得相逢。\n马子章留反诗定把汉兴。\n邓先生搬救兵未见回程。\n那时节君臣们同享太平。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（李大上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "李大",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "买来了萝卜、南瓜、韭菜、葱。"
        },
        {
          "character": "李大",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "老婆子，菜买来了，拿了去做吧。"
        },
        {
          "character": "王氏",
          "line_type": "内白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你问问客人，想吃什么饭？"
        },
        {
          "character": "李大",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "这倒不错。待我问问。\n请问客人，想吃什么饭？"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘秀",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "随便就好。"
        },
        {
          "character": "李大",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "随便，随便。\n老婆子，客人说啦，要吃“随便”，拿了去做吧。"
        },
        {
          "character": "王氏",
          "line_type": "内白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "是。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "众邻人 （内同白） 嗳，李大，打更啦！"
        },
        {
          "character": "李大",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "伙计们，今儿个我店里住了客人啦，没人伺候，你们替我打一夜吧。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "众邻人 （内同白） 也好，叫你老婆同我们歇一夜吧。"
        },
        {
          "character": "李大",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "这是什么话？"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "众邻人 （内同白） 老实话。"
        },
        {
          "character": "李大",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你们先去，我随后就到。\n我说客官，我有话告诉你说：只因王莽坐了天下，出下榜文捉拿妖人刘秀。我\n们这遇龙镇上，家家户户，轮流打更。今天派在我的头上啦。你在店里，不要\n出去，我对你说，这是厨房，饿了有东西吃。这座房是我妹子的房，千万不可\n进去！记着！这座房是我老婆的房，要是闷的慌，串门儿倒不要紧，记清啦。\n我打更去啦。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（李大下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘秀",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "闷煞小王也！"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘秀",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "一见店东他去了，\n不由小王心内焦。\n何日才把愁眉消！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（李月仙上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "李月仙",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "轻移莲步出绣房，\n不由奴家自思量。"
        },
        {
          "character": "李月仙",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "奴家，李月仙。自幼父母双亡，跟随兄嫂长大成人。这且不言。今天上房住了\n一位客人，我看他年纪不大，五官端正，并非平常之人，双眉愁锁，必有什么\n心事在怀。哥哥打更去啦，我不免去至上房，听他说些什么。行行去去，来此\n已是。待我站在窗外，偷听一回。正是："
        },
        {
          "character": "李月仙",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "欲知他人事，且听口中言。"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘秀",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "小王独坐店中好不焦躁人也！"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘秀",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "独坐店房泪双流，\n思想马武统貔貅。\n好与父王报冤仇。\n一统山河方罢休。"
        },
        {
          "character": "但愿莽贼早授首、若得兴汉功成就、李月仙",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "原来是他。\n开门来！"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘秀",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "是哪个？"
        },
        {
          "character": "李月仙",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "开开门就知道啦！"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘秀",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "来了。"
        },
        {
          "character": "李月仙",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "拿住啦！"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘秀",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "拿住什么？"
        },
        {
          "character": "李月仙",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "妖人刘秀！"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘秀",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "小姐，你怎说我是妖人刘秀呢？"
        },
        {
          "character": "李月仙",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你口称小王长，小王短，还说不是吗？"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘秀",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "这个！小王正是刘秀，你不要高声喊叫，小王日后若能兴汉，封你一宫，岂不\n是好？"
        },
        {
          "character": "李月仙",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "既如此，谢主隆恩！"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘秀",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "平身。"
        },
        {
          "character": "李月仙",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "启千岁：在此上房倘若走漏风声，那还了得！随奴到后面小房里安身。"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘秀",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "如此甚好。"
        },
        {
          "character": "李月仙",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "随我来！"
        },
        {
          "character": "李月仙",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "手挽手儿进绣房，\n君妃对面作商量。"
        },
        {
          "character": "李月仙",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "幼主请坐，小妃参贺！"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘秀",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "平身，赐坐！"
        },
        {
          "character": "李月仙",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "谢过千岁！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（王氏上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "王氏",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "急急忙忙，出了厨房；有人若问，我是李大的婆娘。"
        },
        {
          "character": "王氏",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "奴家，王氏。配夫李大。开店度日。只因这几天阴天下雨，没有什么买卖。今\n儿个天晴啦，住了一位客人，进了店来，要吃什么“随便”。我知道“随便”\n是怎么个做法？我杀了一只鸡，剩了些汤汤水水，我想月仙妹子是有病之人，\n不免送给她吃去，保养保养，岂不是好？就是这个主意。来此已是。\n我说妹子，开门来！"
        },
        {
          "character": "李月仙",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "是谁呀？"
        },
        {
          "character": "王氏",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哎呀我的妹子，你病了这么些日子，嫂子我哪一天不来给你送茶送饭，怎么今\n天闹的连嫂子我的声音也听不出来啦？"
        },
        {
          "character": "李月仙",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "原来是嫂子。你要没什么事，就不用进来啦！"
        },
        {
          "character": "王氏",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "快快开门，我有事，给你送东西来啦！"
        },
        {
          "character": "李月仙",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "什么东西？"
        },
        {
          "character": "王氏",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我说妹妹，你不知道，今天咱们店里住了一位客人，他要吃什么“随便”。妹\n妹你也知道，嫂子我什么东西不会做呀？就是这个“随便”差一点儿。倒把我\n给难为坏啦。没办法啦，我杀了一只鸡，糊里糊涂做给那位客人吃了。剩下了\n一些汤汤水水，嫂子我想着给妹妹你是有病之人，吃上点儿，也是保养人的，\n你说好不好？"
        },
        {
          "character": "李月仙",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "多谢嫂子想着小妹。我要用两双筷子。"
        },
        {
          "character": "王氏",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哎哟，你成了姑奶奶啦，你一个人吃饭，怎么用两双筷子哪？说给嫂子听听。"
        },
        {
          "character": "李月仙",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "嫂子有所不知，小妹我如今病体痊愈，要两双筷子，小妹好敬神送圣呀！"
        },
        {
          "character": "王氏",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哎呀！不是妹妹说，嫂子真不知道。早点儿你告诉嫂子，我叫你哥哥再多买点\n儿供菜，敬敬神圣，才是正理。如今说也晚啦，改天咱们多敬一回，等我去取\n两双筷子来。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（王氏下。李月仙关门。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "李月仙",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "幼主在此多住几日，等候救兵才是。"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘秀",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "邓先生到此，小王便要起行。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（王氏上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "王氏",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "怎么又把门关起来啦？开门！"
        },
        {
          "character": "李月仙",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "来了。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（李月仙开门，王氏进门。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "王氏",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "两双筷子在此。"
        },
        {
          "character": "李月仙",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "嫂子出去吧。"
        },
        {
          "character": "王氏",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "嫂子我看你送神。"
        },
        {
          "character": "李月仙",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "小妹送神，你看不得，出去吧。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（李月仙推王氏出，关门。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "王氏",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你看这个丫头。每天见我，有说有笑，我有事，都不让我走。今天怎么见了我\n变颜变色的，这是怎么一回事？莫非她有什么心事吗？嗳，待我来听一听，便\n知明白。"
        },
        {
          "character": "李月仙",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "幼主，请尝这鸡汤可好吗？"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘秀",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "汤水倒好。就是缺少佐料。"
        },
        {
          "character": "王氏",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我给你送酱油来啦。开门！"
        },
        {
          "character": "李月仙",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "来了。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（李月仙开门。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "王氏",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "妹妹你跟谁说话哪？"
        },
        {
          "character": "李月仙",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "嫂子，你听见了吗？"
        },
        {
          "character": "王氏",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "听见啦。"
        },
        {
          "character": "李月仙",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "小妹与神圣说话哪。"
        },
        {
          "character": "王氏",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哎呀！我的妹妹，你也不用哄我，要是有人，你把他放出来，咱们一同玩耍，\n嫂子我瞒着你哥哥，咱们姐俩守着一个，还玩不到天上去吗？"
        },
        {
          "character": "李月仙",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "嫂子别这么胡言乱语，哪我来的什么人？"
        },
        {
          "character": "王氏",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "没有人？想吃独的，你与我走过来！再与我走过去！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（刘秀隐在李月仙身后，被王氏发现。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "王氏",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哎哟！我的妈呀！"
        },
        {
          "character": "王氏",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "一见娃娃怒气发，\n不由王氏咬银牙。\n李大本是好人家。\n霎时叫你染黄沙。"
        },
        {
          "character": "遇龙镇上访一访、怒气不息将你打、李月仙",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "月仙慌忙来跪下，\n尊声嫂嫂听根芽：\n不可喊叫惊吓他。\n登基举家受荣华。"
        },
        {
          "character": "高抬贵手饶恕吧、他本汉朝幼主驾、王氏",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我把你这个丫头，想吃独食，这就叫你吃不成！像这事情，我也不敢自己做主。\n我去把你哥哥叫来，再跟你们俩算帐！这可让出了空儿来啦，你们想怎么玩，\n就怎么玩去吧！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（刘秀、李月仙同下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "王氏",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "唉，李大啊！你妹子……哎呀！这个丑事，我怎么说出来哪！嗳，她做得出来，"
        }
      ],
      "interactions": [
        {
          "edge": "李大→刘秀",
          "turns": 6
        },
        {
          "edge": "刘秀→李大",
          "turns": 5
        },
        {
          "edge": "李大→王氏",
          "turns": 3
        },
        {
