    {
      "scene_index": 2,
      "label": "第二场",
      "characters_present": [
        "恶狠狠钢刀来举起",
        "李大",
        "王氏"
      ],
      "lines": [
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（李大上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "李大",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "鼓打三更半夜交，肩扛棍棒腰带刀。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（王氏内叫喊声。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "李大",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "耳边又听人喊叫，"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（王氏上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "王氏",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "李大啊！快快家来，你妹子房里有了人啦。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（王氏过场，下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "李大",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "想是街坊闹吵吵。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（王氏上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "李大",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哎哟！"
        },
        {
          "character": "李大",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "原来是我的乖乖小娇娇。"
        },
        {
          "character": "王氏",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我说李大呀，今儿个天暖和，我劝你不用戴这个帽子啦！"
        },
        {
          "character": "李大",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我告诉你，天暖也得戴，天寒也得戴。要是不戴，不是让人家就不知道我是怎\n个人了吗？"
        },
        {
          "character": "王氏",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "不戴的好！"
        },
        {
          "character": "李大",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我偏要戴！"
        },
        {
          "character": "王氏",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你既然要戴，李大，你的帽子哪？怎么戴着个和尚帽子？"
        },
        {
          "character": "李大",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "待我来看一看。𠳶！𠳶！再一个𠳶！我把你个臭东西！怎么跑到李大爷头上来\n啦？"
        },
        {
          "character": "王氏",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "李大，你这帽子是在哪里戴来的？"
        },
        {
          "character": "李大",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你问谁呀？"
        },
        {
          "character": "王氏",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "问你！"
        },
        {
          "character": "李大",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "𠳶！𠳶！又是一个𠳶！我把你这个臭蹄子！狗贱人！我不问你，你反来问我，\n这是在你床头上戴来的。"
        },
        {
          "character": "王氏",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "当家的，说了半天，是那个帽子，这你可不用生气呀！这是水月庵和尚的，只\n因四月初八化缘回来，天气温暖，他把帽子放在咱家床上，临走他也忘啦。到\n今儿个也没来取，你知道啦。"
        },
        {
          "character": "李大",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "这也罢啦。我且问你，三更半夜，你不在家里，来到街上吆吆喝喝，见了我摇\n头摆尾，是个什么样儿？"
        },
        {
          "character": "王氏",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "李大，我有话跟你说，你可别生气呀。"
        },
        {
          "character": "李大",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我不生气。"
        },
        {
          "character": "王氏",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你妹子有了丑事啦。"
        },
        {
          "character": "李大",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "慢着！待我来听听。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（〖起三更鼓〗。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "李大",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我把你个婆娘的，我把你个婆娘的！才交半夜子时，你又说起丑时来啦。"
        },
        {
          "character": "王氏",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你不要“子时”“丑时”，我实对你说吧，你妹子心里有了人啦。"
        },
        {
          "character": "李大",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "但不知有了几个？"
        },
        {
          "character": "王氏",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "还有几个？就是一个。"
        },
        {
          "character": "李大",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "一个还好，我不怕，怕的是七八十来个，哎呀，天啊，我的青天、蓝天、月白\n天哪！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（李大卧。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "王氏",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你看看，李大听说他妹子房里有了人，喜得他连蹦带跳，冰冷的地就躺下啦。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（李大起。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "李大",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我把你这个贱人！为丈夫的听了你的话，气得我昏倒在地。你就该走上前来，\n将为丈夫的扶起，后心捶上几掌，叫几声：“我的人！我的肉！我的心肝！我\n的连手！”才是道理。那才称得起“三从四德”，贤惠的媳妇。"
        },
        {
          "character": "王氏",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "既然如此，咱们再重来。李大，你妹子房里有了人啦！"
        },
        {
          "character": "李大",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "有几个？"
        },
        {
          "character": "王氏",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "就是一个。"
        },
        {
          "character": "李大",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "还好，一个我不怕，怕的是七八十来个。哎呀，天啊，我的青天、蓝天、月白\n天哪！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（李大卧。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "王氏",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "嗳，李大，当家的！我的人！我的肉！我的心肝！我的连手！"
        },
        {
          "character": "李大",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "气煞我也！"
        },
        {
          "character": "李大",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "听一言来怒气发，\n不由李大咬钢牙。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（李大、王氏同进门，同望。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "李大",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "一见好像认识他。\n管叫一命染黄沙。"
        },
        {
          "character": "恶狠狠钢刀来举起、王氏",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "当家的，你知道这娃娃是谁？"
        },
        {
          "character": "李大",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我知道，他是我的大儿子。"
        },
        {
          "character": "王氏",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "方才你妹妹告诉我，他是汉朝幼主妖人刘秀！"
        },
        {
          "character": "李大",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "是他吗？好啦，李大要发财啦。"
        },
        {
          "character": "王氏",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "怎么要发财？"
        },
        {
          "character": "李大",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "他既是刘秀，我将他献与莽主，必然封九齐王，岂不发了财吗？"
        },
        {
          "character": "王氏",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "只有三齐王，哪有九齐王啊？"
        },
        {
          "character": "李大",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "莽主见我的功劳大，多封六齐。"
        },
        {
          "character": "王氏",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "罢啦。你可知刘秀手下有两员大将，一个姚期，一个马武，闻听你把刘秀献与\n莽主，岂肯与你干休？把你一把——"
        },
        {
          "character": "李大",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哎哟，我的妈呀！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（李大趴下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "王氏",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你是怎么啦？"
        },
        {
          "character": "李大",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我叫马武抓的。"
        },
        {
          "character": "王氏",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "是我说的，哪儿有马武啊？"
        },
        {
          "character": "李大",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "没有马武，我也好啦。"
        },
        {
          "character": "王氏",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哎呀，就是这个胆子，还敢拿刘秀哪？"
        },
        {
          "character": "李大",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "话要说完，马武一把怎么样？"
        },
        {
          "character": "王氏",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "说了你害怕。"
        },
        {
          "character": "李大",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你说明白啦，我就不怕啦。"
        },
        {
          "character": "王氏",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "不怕啦，他一把抓出你的龟屎来！"
        },
        {
          "character": "李大",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "这个事你看怎么办好哪？"
        },
        {
          "character": "王氏",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "依我的主意，不如将咱们妹子许配幼主，你我也就发了财啦，你岂不是国舅爷\n了吗？"
        },
        {
          "character": "李大",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "只是一件，倘若王莽知道，又怎么好哪？"
        },
        {
          "character": "王氏",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哪能管这许多，你拿主意吧。"
        },
        {
          "character": "李大",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "按你的主意，这么会儿我成了他的大舅子啦，也罢，叫他们两人到里头玩官的\n去吧！我说老婆，咱们妹子做了娘娘，咱们两口子是什么东西？"
        },
        {
          "character": "王氏",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "咱们妹子做了娘娘，你岂不是个国舅爷爷吗？"
        },
        {
          "character": "李大",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我是国舅爷爷，你是什么做的？"
        },
        {
          "character": "王氏",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "这是什么话？我就是国舅奶奶。"
        },
        {
          "character": "李大",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "咱们演习演习看。"
        },
        {
          "character": "王氏",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "好，好！我说那边儿来的敢是国舅爷爷吗？"
        },
        {
          "character": "李大",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "正是。那厢来的可是国舅奶奶吗？"
        },
        {
          "character": "王氏",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "不敢，国舅爷爷请前行。"
        },
        {
          "character": "李大",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "不敢，国舅奶奶请前行。"
        },
        {
          "character": "王氏",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "如此有僭了！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（〖三锣〗。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "王氏",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哎呀！闪了老娘的腰啦！"
        },
        {
          "character": "李大",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "闪了腰事小，不要闪了小国舅！看起来，李大福份不小。\n闲人闪开，天下无双的官大舅子来也！"
        },
        {
          "character": "李大",
          "line_type": "笑",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哈哈哈……"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（李大、王氏同下。）"
        }
      ],
